e> blah</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> want you to go to bazaar and buy necro funeral pyre, or emmisary of thule, or torpor, or malo, or boa, or c3.... I agree on the last 2 the price is coming down but everyone has to pay a heck of a lot for level 60 spells it something you have to deal with, maybe its not fair that druids get the spells easier but its not like wiz are the only ones that get shafted on price of spells and availability.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Torpor - sells for 30k<br>
KEI - sells for 20-30k (pretty common too)<br>
Malo - sells for 20-30k (less common than KEI, but common)<br>
BoA - 20k<br>
...<br>
Sunstrike - 120k (the one time I saw it listed)<br>
<br>
And remember, Sunstrike is but one of our lev 60 nukes. GSS and Elnericks aren't on the market for the most part. Please also note that other lev 59-60 spells like Xuzl and Invert Gravity are also very very rare. I saw Xuzl for 60k the other day. Wizards get hit from every angle on my server (fennin ro).<br>
<br>
Zeg<br>
